ess}/div{\textgreater}{\textless}div id="" class="section"{\textgreater}{\textless}h3 class="{abstractTitle} text-title my-1" id="d68071291e234"{\textgreater}Discussion and conclusions{\textless}/h3{\textgreater}{\textless}p{\textgreater}This study contributes to the small body of literature that has examined the relationship between personality and social networking site addiction and is one of only two studies to examine the addictive use of Instagram and the underlying factors related to it.{\textless}/p{\textgreater}{\textless}/div{\textgreater}{\textless}/section{\textgreater}},
